{"type": "article", "id": 12744, "title": "Apple Watch 壁挂式充电器", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-29T06:36:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000227Mw1ETGCZIOrztgvD.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tApple Watch 问世这段时间，尽管卖得不怎么样，周边产品却层出不穷。给 Apple Watch 充电的底座或简约时尚，或风趣可爱，但目前大部分产品是站立式的。而 Kegan 和 Roberto 设计的这个充电器则是紧紧贴在墙上的。KERO Cling 的设计非常简单，设计师用一个圆环把充电器固定在墙上，而 Apple Watch 靠近充电器，则会被吸附在上面进行充电。可以贴在墙壁上，也可以平放在桌子上，节省空间且十分美观。这是<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/keroproducts/kero-cling-for-apple-watch\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140456907xqKgwOFTLR3Pa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140456uV8rqiE0OpyjQ1vL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66470588\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140457g5qsG4ZSmVIzKWUe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"10.36764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}